quests.desc: Welcome to TextWorld! Here is your task for today. First off, move north. And then, go to the north. With that accomplished, make an effort to venture north. With that accomplished, attempt to head west. That done, take a trip south. Next, try to take a trip south. And then, go to the west. And then, try to take a trip west. With that over with, make an attempt to head north. With that over with, recover the latchkey from the cabinet within the bathroom. And if you do that, you're the winner!

objective: Hey, thanks for coming over to the TextWorld today, there is something I need you to do for me. First of all, go north. And then, attempt to go north. And then, make an effort to go to the north. With that over with, attempt to go west. Then, travel south. After that, make an attempt to go south. With that over with, make an attempt to travel west. And then, make an effort to go to the west. Then, try to move north. After that, retrieve the latchkey from the cabinet. And if you do that, you're the winner!
